   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="abstract" resp="vh">
            <p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_III_3929">
                  <rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person"
                        ref="pe__johann_oeczesdorffer_facs_164_TextRegion_1649940629992_858">Hanns
                        Öczestorffer, der <roleName type="prof">kürsnergesell</roleName>, <rs
                           type="person" ref="pe__andreas_oeczesdorffer_QGW_II_II_2627">Andres des
                           Öczestorffer <roleName type="dead">seligen</roleName></rs>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__andreas_oeczesdorffer_QGW_II_II_2627"
                           >sun</roleName></rs></rs>, gibt seinem <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs
                        type="person" ref="pe__konrad_oeczestorffer_QGW_II_II_2627"><roleName
                           type="kin"
                           corresp="pe__johann_oeczesdorffer_facs_164_TextRegion_1649940629992_858"
                           >Vetter</roleName> Conraten Öczestorffer, dem <roleName type="prof"
                           >kürsner</roleName>, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien"
                           >burger</roleName> zu Wienn</rs></rs>, allen seinen tail erbschaft und
                  gerechtigkait . . . an aim haus, gelegen undern Satlern zu Wienn zunagst Balthers,
                  des satler, haus, auf. </rs></p>
         </div>
         <div type="seal">
            <p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_III_3929">Besiegelt mit den Siegeln <rs type="fn"
                     role="witness"><rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_ernst_QGW_II_III_3758"
                        >Niclasen des Ernsten <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien"
                              ><add>burger</add></roleName></rs> und <rs type="person"
                        ref="pe__johann_ravensburger_QGW_II_II_3264">Hannsen des Ravenspurger,
                           <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">urtailschreiber</roleName>,
                        baider <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">burger</roleName> zu
                        Wienn</rs></rs> . </rs></p>
         </div>
